+- `GET /health` -> health check in [`air-mentor-api/src/app.ts`](../../air-mentor-api/src/app.ts)
+- `GET /openapi.json` -> Swagger/OpenAPI in [`air-mentor-api/src/app.ts`](../../air-mentor-api/src/app.ts)
+
