+
+Defined in [`air-mentor-api/src/modules/academic-proof-routes.ts`](../../air-mentor-ui/air-mentor-api/src/modules/academic-proof-routes.ts) and backed by [`src/system-admin-live-data.ts`](../../src/system-admin-live-data.ts) route state.
