ifferently by role, route, active run, or checkpoint context, record separate variants\\naudit-map/20-prompts/prompt-change-log.md:8:| 2026-04-15 | route-map-pass.md, role-surface-pass.md, feature-atom-pass.md, dependency-pass.md, data-flow-pass.md, state-flow-pass.md, ml-audit-pass.md, test-gap-pass.md, ux-friction-pass.md, live-behavior-pass.md, audit-the-audit-pass.md, synthesis-pass.md | Upgraded pass prompts to v2.0 with explicit exhaustiveness and evidence requirements | Prevent shallow route, role, feature, state, and live mapping |\\naudit-map/31-queues/audit-air-mentor-ui-bootstrap-inventory-pass.prompt.md:23:Objective: enumerate the scoped files, routes, scripts, configs, and evidence sources without over-interpreting behavior.\\naudit-map/20-prompts/inventory-pass.md:3:Objective: enumerate the scoped files, routes, scripts, configs, and evidence sources without over-interpreting behavior.\\naudit-map/20-prompts/audit-the-audit-pass.md:10:- coverage diff by route, role, feature, dependency, data, state, ML, test, UX, and live evidence family\\naudit-map/20-prompts/role-surface-pass.md:9:- route guards, data-visibility rules, backend authorization rules, and cross-role truth-coupling notes\\nair-mentor-api/src/lib/msruas-proof-control-plane.ts:842:  let hash = 2166136261\\nair-mentor-api/src/lib/msruas-proof-control-plane.ts:844:    hash ^= char.charCodeAt(0)\\nair-mentor-api/src/lib/msruas-proof-control-plane.ts:845:    hash = Math.imul(hash, 16777619)\\nair-mentor-api/src/lib/msruas-proof-control-plane.ts:847:  return (hash >>> 0) / 4294967295\\naudit-map/23-coverage/review-status-by-path.md:5:| `src/` | Mapped | Frontend hash routes and internal navigation entry points cataloged |\\naudit-map/23-coverage/review-status-by-path.md:6:| `src/pages/` | Mapped | Page module inventory captured; route behavior mapping completed |\\naudit-map/23-coverage/review-status-by-path.md:8:| `air-mentor-api/src/` | Mapped | Backend topology known; endpoint and inference a